transcripts:
[MUSIC PLAYING]

Flaunt your style and protect your phone with a slim, sophisticated, and strong symmetry series for the iPhone 6. Boasting sleek, clean construction, this stunning one-piece case is simple to install. Style may be new fro Otterbox, but protection isn't. The dual material construction makes symmetry series one of the most protective and slimmest cases in its class. The raised edge around the screen helps keep every inch of the beautiful 4.7 inch display protected. While the softer internal material and patterned coring absorb shock keeping it away from your iPhone 6. A full spectrum of wrap-around colors and graphics makes this case your canvas for design. The Symmetry series is the style you want with the protection you need
